# Logs
logs
*.log

# Prisma
/prisma/generated-client
query-engine*
# migration_lock.toml is intentionally committed (Prisma best practice — pins the
# migration provider so a fresh clone's `migrate deploy` is self-contained).

# OS Files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Runtime data — patient uploads (PDFs, photos, screenshots).
# Contains PII; must not be committed. The previous entries here
# were saved with the wrong encoding (UTF-16) and were silently
# ignored by git, which is why these files kept appearing as
# untracked despite the rule being present.
uploads/

# One-off maintenance scripts kept locally only.
# Specific filename rather than *.mjs so the verification scripts
# under scripts/verify-*-fixes.mjs are not accidentally ignored.
update-passwords.mjs

# RAG corpus artefact — regenerated by scripts/buildRagIndex.js.
# Source markdown (topic-passages.md) is committed; the embedded
# vector file is not (large, regenerable, costs cents to rebuild).
data/ragCorpus/corpus.json
